<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Na caan tha te'n hmang tuah, Na Bawipa chawn tuah, Amah cu zungzal in,
 Fek tein zum tuah, Pathian fale khawm hna, Zaang tlawmmi bawm hna, A van
 thluachuahnak cu, Na hmuh khawh nakhnga.

[V2]
 Na caan tha te'n hmang tuah, Vawlei a dong lio, Na caan sung vialte
 cu, Jesuh he hmang ko, Jesuh bang si awkah, Amah i zohchun, Na tuahmi
 rian kipah, Amah bantukin.

[V3]
 Na caan tha te'n hmang tuah, Na hruaitu siseh, A sinah zeitik hmanh,
 Then loin um tuah Lawmh le ngaihchiat zongah, Amah cu zul ko, Jesuh lei
 kha zoh law, A bia kha zum ko.

[V4]
 Na caan tha te'n hmang tuah, Dai tein um tuah, Na ruahmi thil kip kha,
 Amah nawl siseh, Nunnak tikhor ah khin, Nangmah an hruai lai, Van zongah
 khin a rian, Na tuan khawhnak lai.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>NA CAAN THA TEIN HMANG TUAH CH301</title>
<hymn_number>301</hymn_number>
</song>